about.summary: A wrapper for the Agrum library, to make flexible and scalable probabilistic graphical models.

name: pyagrum
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.13.2" %}

package:
  name: pyagrum
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: pyagrum-{{ version }}.tar.bz2
  url: https://gitlab.com/agrumery/aGrUM/repository/archive.tar.bz2?ref={{ version }}
  sha256: d424dc35ebf2b3d3a36f4c76bc6bf8fdc635ebbbe5aa2953a091ef0baa8a8086

build:
  number: 1

requirements:
  build:
    - cmake
    - {{ compiler('c') }}  # [unix]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}  # [unix]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}  # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}  # [win]
  host:
    - python
    - libpython  # [win]
    - numpy
  run:
    - python
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - pydotplus
    - matplotlib

test:
  requires:
    - ipython
  imports:
    - pyAgrum
    - pyAgrum.lib.bn2roc
    - pyAgrum.lib.bn2scores
    - pyAgrum.lib.bn_vs_bn
    - pyAgrum.lib.dynamicBN
    - pyAgrum.lib.notebook
    - pyAgrum.lib.pretty_print
  source_files:
    - wrappers/pyAgrum/testunits/
  commands:
    - python wrappers/pyAgrum/testunits/gumTest.py

about:
  home: http://agrum.gitlab.io/
  license: GPL3
  license_file: COPYRIGHT.txt
  summary: A wrapper for the Agrum library, to make flexible and scalable probabilistic graphical models.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jschueller
    - ltorti
